      DIRECTORY ARE LIMITED TO ONLY 5 MINUTES OF USE.

      Unlike official versions,  when  you  run  each  software  of  'SUITE
      GESTACOMPTE', there is a delay.

      For a good use of  that  demo  version  of  'SUITE  GESTACOMPTE',  we
      recommend you to click on the icon 'MakeAssign'.


