                                    -***-

 LANGUAGE :

 Softwares of that pack are localised.

 At present, only French and English are available.

 If you want you can translate the softwares into another language (.catalog)
 and redistribute  them on an 'AMINET' site.

 In addition to that, you have to send us your translations.

 We are searching for translators into any language for GestaCompte Suite. If
 you  are  interessed, please  contact Marie-Christine at (33) 05 56 05 72 09
 for more details.

                                    -***-


 PRESENTATION & ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS :


 'SUITE  GESTACOMPTE'  was  conceived   to   make   easier   commercial   and
 administrative  management  of  your  profession.  This  suite  is specially
 intended for little firms, tradesmen, artisan or independents.

 The author and co-ordinators  wanted  'SUITE  GESTACOMPTE'  approachable  by
 everyone,  neophyte  or  professional.  So  they tried to make each software
 interface as agreeable as possible. Each interface is conceived on the  same
 pattern, so user is not disoriented.

 Each software of 'SUITE GESTACOMPTE' is independent, so  everyone  can  make
 his own pack according to his need.

 Each software of this suite is  multi-tasking  and  entirely  respect  AMIGA
 system.

 'SUITE GESTACOMPTE' moves very quickly, due, in part, to  previous  versions
 users  who  sent  us  suggestions, criticals, etc... We can't enumerate them
 here, but we thank them all.

 As they did, you can help 'SUITE GESTACOMPTE' development. We are hopping to
 hear of you. Thanks.


                                    -***-


 LIMITS OF THOSE VERSIONS :


 SOFTWARES ONLY RUN UNDER WORKBENCH 2.0 OR MORE.

 Softwares in that pack are  fully  operational,  but  they  are  limited  in
 utilisation :

  - A delay when you run softwares,
  - Only 5 minutes of use, then you have to run again the software,
  - Preferences backup desable.
  - Exclusively year 1998 data backup.
  - Account Add/Modif desable.
  - Word processing printind desable.

 In spite of those limitations of use, we  hope  you  can  well  test  'SUITE
 GESTACOMPTE' and appreciate quality and seriousness of this product.


